    diagram_server_network["GameWebSocketServer<br/>server/src/network/websocket.ts<br/>Owns: clients map • player socket registry<br/>Ingress: join • move • say • start_convo • input_start • input_stop • end_convo<br/>Egress: player_joined • player_update • convo_update • message<br/>Depends On: GameLoop • protocol.ts unions<br/>Internals: broadcastGameEvent() • toPublicPlayer() • participant-scoped convo sends"]
    diagram_server_debug["Debug API<br/>Express router<br/>Owns: GET debug routes • POST debug routes<br/>Ingress: GET /state • GET /map • GET /players • GET /log • GET /conversations • GET /memories/:playerId • POST /tick • POST /spawn • POST /move • POST /input • POST /scenario • POST /start-convo • POST /say • POST /end-convo<br/>Egress: JSON snapshots • queued engine mutations • direct conversation mutations<br/>Depends On: GameLoop • scenario presets<br/>Internals: renderAsciiMap() • scenario loader"]
    diagram_server_engine["ENGINE<br/>I/O-free simulation core<br/>Owns: players_ • heldKeys_ • commandQueue_ • afterTickCallbacks • eventHandlers<br/>Ingress: spawn • move_to • start_convo • say • end_convo • setPlayerInput()<br/>Egress: spawn • player_update • input_state • convo_started • convo_active • convo_ended<br/>Depends On: pathfinding (A* + heap) • collision (AABB tile) • SeededRNG<br/>Internals: GameLoop • World • ConversationManager • GameLogger<br/>World (world.ts): tiles[][] • activities • spawnPoints<br/>ConversationManager (conversation.ts): conversations • playerToConvo • nextId<br/>GameLogger (logger.ts): circular buffer (1000 events)"]
    diagram_server_npc["NPC STACK<br/>server/src/npc/*<br/>Owns: reply scheduling • memory retrieval • reflection triggers<br/>Ingress: spawn • convo_started • convo_active • convo_ended • tick_complete<br/>Egress: start_convo • say • memory upserts<br/>Depends On: Claude CLI subprocess • scripted fallback • placeholder embeddings<br/>Internals: NpcOrchestrator • MemoryManager • Provider Stack<br/>NpcOrchestrator (orchestrator.ts): reply scheduling • initiation scans • reflection triggering • persistence coordination<br/>MemoryManager (memory.ts): composite scoring • reflection logic • conversation summarization<br/>Provider Stack (provider.ts / resilientProvider.ts): NpcModelProvider interface • ResilientNpcProvider • ClaudeCodeProvider • ScriptedNpcProvider"]
    diagram_server_persistence["PERSISTENCE<br/>server/src/db/*<br/>Owns: Repository implementations • Npc store implementations • schema + vector index<br/>Ingress: memory writes • conversation snapshots • player/NPC snapshots<br/>Egress: memory search results • restored NPC state<br/>Depends On: in-memory fallback • Postgres + pgvector<br/>Internals: MemoryStore • NpcPersistenceStore • PostgreSQL + pgvector<br/>MemoryStore (repository.ts): Repository (Postgres) • InMemoryRepository<br/>NpcPersistenceStore (npcStore.ts): PostgresNpcStore • InMemoryNpcStore<br/>PostgreSQL + pgvector (schema.sql): 8 tables • vector(1536) • IVFFlat memory index"]
  end
